1
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:32,640
[Episode 1]

2
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:32,742
You can never escape us.

3
00:05:00,729 --> 00:05:02,349
Your Highness!

4
00:05:03,842 --> 00:05:06,561
Your Majesty. Princess Rong Le is awake.

5
00:05:06,561 --> 00:05:08,317
Your Majesty.

6
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,474
Come on.

7
00:05:22,014 --> 00:05:23,946
Even if you disagree with this marriage alliance,

8
00:05:23,946 --> 00:05:26,446
you shouldn't have run away on your own.

9
00:05:26,446 --> 00:05:28,839
You have been wounded and blamed.

10
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,598
Are you happy now?

11
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,732
Who are you?

12
00:05:35,733 --> 00:05:37,773
What is this place?

13
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,500
Rong Le.

14
00:05:42,946 --> 00:05:47,327
Your Majesty, Physician Liu's worry came true.

15
00:05:47,327 --> 00:05:49,820
Her Highness might have had a concussion.

16
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:52,855
That is why she lost her memories.

17
00:05:52,855 --> 00:05:55,540
- Your Highness?
- What are you talking about?

18
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:58,099
I lost my memories?

19
00:05:58,099 --> 00:06:00,440
I don't understand a thing you say.

20
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,951
You are in the royal palace of Western Qi.

21
00:06:02,951 --> 00:06:06,020
I am the Emperor of Western Qi.

22
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:08,040
You are my younger sister.

23
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:10,530
You are Princess Rong Le of this nation.

24
00:06:13,546 --> 00:06:15,152
I am...

25
00:06:16,044 --> 00:06:18,900
Princess Rong Le of Western Qi?

26
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:20,500
Yes.

27
00:06:22,139 --> 00:06:23,679
Your Majesty.

28
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:27,279
The medicine is ready.

29
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:36,336
Don't be worried about this.

30
00:06:36,336 --> 00:06:38,370
According to the physician,

31
00:06:38,370 --> 00:06:42,739
as long as you take your medicine on time, you will slowly regain your memories.

32
00:06:44,409 --> 00:06:45,969
Take your medicine.

33
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,480
I am not drinking this.

34
00:07:02,609 --> 00:07:04,269
It's all right.

35
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:09,280
You just woke up, you must be feeling a little discomfort.

36
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:11,380
Stay here and rest well.

37
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:13,846
You may drink it when you wish to.

38
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:29,166
Little Xun.

39
00:07:47,336 --> 00:07:48,919
Rong Le,

40
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,866
you have my word.

41
00:07:50,866 --> 00:07:54,179
I will do whatever it takes to help you regain your memories.

42
00:07:54,179 --> 00:07:58,441
Calm down and get well.

43
00:07:59,818 --> 00:08:01,277
You are dismissed.

44
00:08:01,277 --> 00:08:03,500
Let the princess have some rest.

45
00:08:05,759 --> 00:08:07,559
Yes.

46
00:08:24,580 --> 00:08:26,514
Rong Le?

47
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:29,550
Princess?

48
00:08:30,634 --> 00:08:32,614
Marriage arrangement?

49
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:36,280
Amnesia?

50
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:38,236
An emperor for brother?

51
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:44,020
Why can't I remember any of these?

52
00:08:45,115 --> 00:08:47,001
Who exactly am I?

53
00:09:11,034 --> 00:09:14,030
- Is this where I lived?
- Yes, Your Highness.

54
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:15,900
You are His Majesty's only sister.

55
00:09:15,900 --> 00:09:18,117
His Majesty loves you very much.

56
00:09:18,118 --> 00:09:20,251
No matter how busy His Majesty is with the nation's affairs,

57
00:09:20,252 --> 00:09:23,775
whether it has been days or longer, he will be here to visit you.

58
00:09:23,775 --> 00:09:25,816
Your Highness is very clingy to His Majesty, too.

59
00:09:25,816 --> 00:09:27,216
Your Highness—

60
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,757
Your Highness?

61
00:09:30,616 --> 00:09:32,202
Your Highness?

62
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,868
Your Highness.

63
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:38,414
Your Highness.

64
00:09:39,867 --> 00:09:42,047
Am I really a princess?

65
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:45,519
Your Highness!

66
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:49,647
Your Highness, why are you here? Are you all right?

67
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:52,890
Your Highness.

68
00:09:53,756 --> 00:09:55,261
Your Highness?

69
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,742
Your Majesty.

70
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,333
You seem to be feeling better now.

71
00:10:01,333 --> 00:10:04,862
I promised you I will help you find the memories.

72
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:11,819
I can help you regain the lost memories if you want.

73
00:10:11,819 --> 00:10:16,863
However, if you act recklessly like you were just now...

74
00:10:16,863 --> 00:10:19,045
and charge right into everything,

75
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,569
not only will it not help,

76
00:10:22,569 --> 00:10:24,709
you will even get hurt and lectured.

77
00:10:24,709 --> 00:10:27,171
Please, refrain yourself from doing that.

78
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:36,400
This was your favorite place once.

79
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:38,817
It feels familiar, does it?

80
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:47,540
Does it remind you of something?

81
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:55,002
Rong Le,

82
00:10:55,805 --> 00:11:00,083
back in the days, you loved to brew tea in this room.

83
00:11:00,083 --> 00:11:02,816
You were great at brewing tea.

84
00:11:02,816 --> 00:11:06,588
No one in the whole palace can best your skills.

85
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:09,000
Let's give it a try.

86
00:11:51,378 --> 00:11:53,211
You should try, too.

87
00:12:00,070 --> 00:12:01,576
How is it?

88
00:12:02,802 --> 00:12:05,959
See? You may have lost your memories,

89
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,614
but I think...

90
00:12:07,614 --> 00:12:11,619
the muscle memories for your interests still remain.

91
00:12:11,619 --> 00:12:14,479
Rong Le, don't worry about this.

92
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:16,746
Everything will be back to normal.

93
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:25,873
These are your favorite desserts.

94
00:12:26,512 --> 00:12:28,155
Give them a try.

95
00:12:41,907 --> 00:12:43,350
It's okay.

96
00:12:43,350 --> 00:12:45,051
One step at a time.

97
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:55,296
Let me play you a song.

98
00:12:55,296 --> 00:12:57,999
It was once the song you loved the most.

99
00:12:58,560 --> 00:13:01,577
You always asked me to play it for you.

100
00:13:01,577 --> 00:13:03,619
I always think...

101
00:13:03,620 --> 00:13:08,370
the time we spent playing melodies and brewing tea...

102
00:13:08,370 --> 00:13:10,923
were the happiest moments of our life.

103
00:13:57,475 --> 00:14:00,427
"So that reminiscence does not linger,

104
00:14:01,025 --> 00:14:04,032
so that sorrow never lasts."

105
00:14:22,680 --> 00:14:25,597
Why is this written in different handwriting?

106
00:14:26,583 --> 00:14:28,629
Your Highness.

107
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:33,162
Your Highness, it's time to take your medicine.

108
00:14:36,575 --> 00:14:38,106
Ling Yue.

109
00:14:38,106 --> 00:14:40,656
Can you tell if I wrote this poem?

110
00:14:43,554 --> 00:14:45,918
Yes, you wrote this.

111
00:14:45,918 --> 00:14:48,547
I was there when you wrote this.

112
00:14:49,301 --> 00:14:51,688
All right, Your Highness.

113
00:14:51,688 --> 00:14:54,879
Come on, finish this medicine.

114
00:14:54,879 --> 00:14:56,740
I will drink it later.

115
00:14:58,267 --> 00:15:01,180
The Empress Dowager arrives!

116
00:15:01,180 --> 00:15:05,007
Come on, Your Highness. We should be kneeling.

117
00:15:25,020 --> 00:15:26,868
Arrest her.

118
00:15:30,409 --> 00:15:32,578
What do you want? Let go of me!

119
00:15:32,578 --> 00:15:33,959
Why are you arresting me?

120
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:37,900
The alliance of Western Qi and Northern Lin is a reality.

121
00:15:37,900 --> 00:15:42,319
You are going to the Northern Lin whether you like it or not!

122
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,901
Seize her!

123
00:15:51,400 --> 00:15:53,314
Your Majesty.

124
00:15:53,314 --> 00:15:55,020
Mother, please calm down.

125
00:15:55,020 --> 00:15:58,303
Rong Le broke the rules because she has amnesia.

126
00:15:58,303 --> 00:16:01,736
She must fulfill this marriage with or without her memories.

127
00:16:01,736 --> 00:16:04,586
Mother, Northern Lin is far from here.

128
00:16:04,586 --> 00:16:07,556
She might never have a chance to return if she leaves.

129
00:16:07,556 --> 00:16:11,672
Rong Le is hurt and suffering from injury. It's only reasonable if she refuses to go.

130
00:16:11,672 --> 00:16:15,279
As for the marriage arrangement, maybe we should delay it.

131
00:16:15,279 --> 00:16:18,380
The army of Chen is advancing on our borders.

132
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:20,836
There are still skirmishes within our land.

133
00:16:20,836 --> 00:16:22,519
We have no means to fight the enemies.

134
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:24,963
The fate of this nation is hanging by a thread.

135
00:16:24,964 --> 00:16:28,819
If we ally with Northern Lin, Chen will be pincered by both of our nations.

136
00:16:28,819 --> 00:16:30,761
They will retreat tactically.

137
00:16:30,762 --> 00:16:32,946
I simply don't understand.

138
00:16:32,946 --> 00:16:36,890
Why are you still hesitating on making a decision?

139
00:16:36,890 --> 00:16:40,719
As for the war with Chen, I will come up with a strategy.

140
00:16:40,719 --> 00:16:43,439
But Rong Le is suffering from wounds and amnesia.

141
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:46,999
The matter with the marriage needs more time to be considered.

142
00:16:46,999 --> 00:16:51,396
In the end, it's all about her.

143
00:16:53,239 --> 00:16:59,239
I was kind enough to spare your life and crowned you the princess.

144
00:16:59,239 --> 00:17:05,262
Now, I still have the power to make you die a slow death.

145
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:08,034
Mother, please show mercy.

146
00:17:08,600 --> 00:17:10,815
The date for the wedding is a week from now.

147
00:17:10,815 --> 00:17:15,276
I shall order a servant to place that poison wine in the main hall.

148
00:17:15,276 --> 00:17:18,661
Mother, why must you do this?

149
00:17:18,661 --> 00:17:22,500
You can either send her on a palaquin to Northern Lin...

150
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:27,550
or you can prepare for my funeral a week from now.

151
00:17:27,550 --> 00:17:29,871
The choice is yours.

152
00:17:36,991 --> 00:17:38,959
Your Majesty.

153
00:17:44,660 --> 00:17:46,241
Rong Le!

154
00:17:49,399 --> 00:17:50,842
Rong Le?

155
00:17:57,020 --> 00:18:00,108
- What do you want?
- Don't be afraid.

156
00:18:00,109 --> 00:18:02,691
I will not send you away for a marriage alliance.

157
00:18:02,691 --> 00:18:04,700
I will sneak you out of here now.

158
00:18:12,887 --> 00:18:16,938
Fear not. I am taking you to a place.

159
00:18:16,938 --> 00:18:18,920
Once you are there,

160
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:21,957
everything will be clear to you.

161
00:19:13,340 --> 00:19:16,263
You lived here for quite a while once.

162
00:19:17,060 --> 00:19:19,212
You liked this place.

163
00:19:23,804 --> 00:19:25,572
Do you like it?

164
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:44,695
"So that reminiscence does not linger, so that sorrow never lasts."

165
00:19:45,980 --> 00:19:47,901
How did you know?

166
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:52,572
Are you suspecting that...

167
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:57,853
these words weren't written by your hands?

168
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:02,979
Come with me.

169
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:16,198
These handwritings seem similar to mine.

170
00:20:16,198 --> 00:20:20,039
The writings on the wall are mine.

171
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:23,999
Rong Le, you were very fond of my handwriting.

172
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:26,346
You always tried to copy the way I wrote.

173
00:20:39,580 --> 00:20:44,163
The words on these papers... are the writings you copied...

174
00:20:44,163 --> 00:20:46,763
while you had free time.

175
00:21:02,152 --> 00:21:05,616
This little hut does feel familiar to me.

176
00:21:05,617 --> 00:21:09,020
If I were a delicate princess that grew up in the palace,

177
00:21:09,020 --> 00:21:13,764
why does it feel so alien to me?

178
00:21:13,765 --> 00:21:16,589
You were born and raised in the Cold Harem.

179
00:21:17,022 --> 00:21:21,180
Your mother was a peasant with mesmerizing beauty.

180
00:21:21,180 --> 00:21:24,211
But she offended my father and was banished.

181
00:21:24,211 --> 00:21:26,712
She was already pregnant with you.

182
00:21:26,712 --> 00:21:30,533
Eight months later, she gave birth to you in the Cold Harem.

183
00:21:32,515 --> 00:21:35,944
That is why Empress Dowager was so mean to me.

184
00:21:36,659 --> 00:21:38,432
She went through an accident.

185
00:21:38,432 --> 00:21:40,119
Her face was scarred.

186
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:42,132
It changed her personality as well.

187
00:21:46,885 --> 00:21:48,445
I see.

188
00:21:52,483 --> 00:21:56,229
Rong Le, you suffered a lot in the past.

189
00:21:56,229 --> 00:21:58,878
But you were stubborn.

190
00:21:59,600 --> 00:22:03,446
A royal guard once received the kindness of your mother.

191
00:22:03,447 --> 00:22:05,839
During your time in the Cold Harem,

192
00:22:05,840 --> 00:22:08,886
you secretly learned some martial arts from him.

193
00:22:09,940 --> 00:22:13,768
So, I wasn't some kind of delicate lady at all.

194
00:22:13,768 --> 00:22:16,595
That is why I have so many calluses on my hand.

195
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:23,628
When we first met each other,

196
00:22:23,628 --> 00:22:26,252
we were still children.

197
00:22:26,252 --> 00:22:28,924
I remember you said that...

198
00:22:28,925 --> 00:22:30,804
"If anyone ever tries to pick on you,

199
00:22:30,804 --> 00:22:34,115
I will be the first to stand up for you."

200
00:22:35,187 --> 00:22:37,755
Why didn't you tell me any of these earlier?

201
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,819
Rong Le,

202
00:22:40,820 --> 00:22:44,201
I don't really want you to remember these unpleasant memories.

203
00:22:44,201 --> 00:22:48,614
But I never thought... you would grow suspicious of me.

204
00:22:50,900 --> 00:22:54,352
The genesis of thoughts is nothing but an illusion.

205
00:22:54,352 --> 00:22:56,984
You need to trust your heart.

206
00:22:56,984 --> 00:22:59,383
You must believe that...

207
00:22:59,383 --> 00:23:04,133
I am the person that wishes to see you happy the most.

208
00:23:21,720 --> 00:23:26,989
Rong Le, these were your favorite flowers.

209
00:24:31,264 --> 00:24:34,669
What's wrong? Are you all right?

210
00:24:34,669 --> 00:24:38,237
- Are you all right?
- I am fine.

211
00:24:38,237 --> 00:24:39,744
Your Majesty!

212
00:24:39,744 --> 00:24:42,429
Your Majesty, I must send you back now.

213
00:24:42,430 --> 00:24:44,455
Take Rong Le with you.

214
00:24:44,455 --> 00:24:46,319
You are severely wounded, we must go now!

215
00:24:46,320 --> 00:24:48,602
Take Rong Le with you and go!

216
00:24:48,603 --> 00:24:50,207
Yes.

217
00:25:01,338 --> 00:25:03,075
Are you all right?

218
00:25:04,180 --> 00:25:06,859
Brother! Wake up!

219
00:25:06,859 --> 00:25:11,033
Brother! Xiao Sha, head back to the palace! Hurry up!

220
00:25:11,033 --> 00:25:12,519
Yes!

221
00:25:43,700 --> 00:25:47,826
Your Majesty wished to cheer Princess Rong Le up...

222
00:25:47,827 --> 00:25:50,779
and even took the risk of sneaking her out of the palace.

223
00:25:50,779 --> 00:25:54,630
But you were ambushed by the assassins of Chen.

224
00:25:54,630 --> 00:25:57,905
Are you happy now?

225
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:03,316
Take Xiao Sha out of here. Punish him with eighty beatings.

226
00:26:03,316 --> 00:26:05,764
Thank you for sparing my life.

227
00:26:09,670 --> 00:26:11,358
Stop.

228
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:14,253
Come with me.

229
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:31,590
[Yongyang Palace]

230
00:26:41,940 --> 00:26:44,979
As of now, the land is in turmoil.

231
00:26:44,979 --> 00:26:46,999
War ravages the nation.

232
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:50,739
The land of Qi is not rich with resources.

233
00:26:50,739 --> 00:26:53,018
Our army is weak.

234
00:26:53,019 --> 00:26:56,419
The national treasury is almost empty because of the war.

235
00:26:56,419 --> 00:26:59,245
We should be having peace to recover from the loss.

236
00:26:59,245 --> 00:27:01,876
But as you can see now,

237
00:27:01,877 --> 00:27:05,327
all the new recruits in the army...

238
00:27:05,327 --> 00:27:08,690
are either too old or ill for battle.

239
00:27:08,690 --> 00:27:12,959
Sending them to face the force of Wei and Chen...

240
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:16,534
is as good as a suicide mission.

241
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:25,811
It's either the marriage... or the war with enemies?

242
00:27:25,811 --> 00:27:28,416
Correct.

243
00:27:28,416 --> 00:27:33,141
If you can feel no guilt while they are sent to their deaths,

244
00:27:33,141 --> 00:27:36,241
if you can bear to see His Majesty fight for this nation...

245
00:27:36,241 --> 00:27:38,410
despite all the pain he is carrying...

246
00:27:38,410 --> 00:27:44,442
and in the end have his head hanging over the city gate,

247
00:27:45,909 --> 00:27:48,139
then I hope...

248
00:27:48,139 --> 00:27:52,729
you can live to be a witness of this tragedy.

249
00:28:31,840 --> 00:28:34,515
Why did you come back?

250
00:28:36,740 --> 00:28:40,080
It would be nearly impossible to leave the palace again.

251
00:28:40,964 --> 00:28:42,601
Drink the medicine.

252
00:29:03,060 --> 00:29:07,740
[A Clean Heart is as White as Snow]

253
00:29:08,470 --> 00:29:12,199
Your Majesty, we are short on troops and crops.

254
00:29:12,200 --> 00:29:14,379
The people are running out of resources.

255
00:29:14,379 --> 00:29:18,139
The marriage alliance with Northern Lin can save us.

256
00:29:18,139 --> 00:29:21,599
Your Majesty, the marriage is the best viable plan we have.

257
00:29:21,599 --> 00:29:23,438
If Your Majesty is unwilling to give up the princess,

258
00:29:23,438 --> 00:29:27,386
I shall gladly send my daughter instead.

259
00:29:27,387 --> 00:29:29,523
I cannot allow that!

260
00:29:32,360 --> 00:29:34,419
Silence, all of you!

261
00:29:35,130 --> 00:29:37,488
The peace of Qi...

262
00:29:37,488 --> 00:29:40,392
is not to be traded with a woman's life!

263
00:29:40,392 --> 00:29:42,630
Your Majesty, for the sake of Qi,

264
00:29:42,630 --> 00:29:45,907
I shall send my daughter in Her Highness' place.

265
00:29:45,908 --> 00:29:47,680
I am willing to do the same.

266
00:29:47,681 --> 00:29:49,241
You...

267
00:29:51,820 --> 00:29:53,940
[A Clean Heart is as White as Snow]

268
00:29:59,720 --> 00:30:03,623
Need I remind you... that I am the Princess of Qi!

