331
00:36:55,723 --> 00:36:57,686
is Prince Li of Northern Lin.

332
00:36:57,687 --> 00:37:00,130
He is the favorite son of the emperor.

333
00:37:00,131 --> 00:37:03,555
I heard he has a dashing look and strong figure.

334
00:37:03,556 --> 00:37:06,951
Lian Xin, if Prince Li is such a great person,

335
00:37:06,951 --> 00:37:09,340
